Requirements for system registered library materials (version 1.1 / 2017.03.19)

Each library material

Object "Resource"

fields:

 Long resourceID - default;
 ResourceType type (enums: BOOK, MAGAZINE, JOURNAL etc.;
 String title;
 String author;
 int releaseYear;
 /todo Reservation reservation;

1. must have 'unique identifier'
2. must have 'material type' (e.g. book, reference works, periodical articles)
3. must record material basic information (e.g. title, release year etc)
4. must record usage (borrowing) history (when, who, for how long)